Arteta: &quot;After conceding the goal we disorganised ourselves in the high press. We didn't give ourselves a chance to get set in the final third, because we weren't precise on the ball as well.&quot;<br />
<br />
Arteta on Ceballos red card: &quot;We talked at half time that we have to be careful. I was going to take him off and by the time Gabi was ready to come on, that action happened and he was out.&quot;

